Requirements

The game shall display a title screen with the game name and a Start Game action.

The game shall begin gameplay within 1 second of selecting Start Game.

The frog shall move exactly one grid tile per input in the direction selected (up, down, left, right).

The game shall prevent the frog from moving outside the playfield boundaries.

The game shall include at least 5 traffic lanes with vehicles that move horizontally across the screen.

Vehicles shall spawn at configurable intervals per lane-.

The game shall deduct 1 life when the frog collides with any vehicle.

The game shall include a river zone containing floating platforms that move horizontally.

If the frog is in the river zone and is not on a platform tile, the game shall deduct 1 life.

If the frog is on a platform tile, the frog shall move with the platform at the platformâ€™s speed and direction until the frog moves off it.
